yellow or &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; yellow is a 2006 futuristic short film by director neill blomkamp , written by terri &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and blomkamp . it was produced at the request of &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; maker adidas as a part of its " &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; " viral ads campaign , in which advertising agency &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; gathered seven directors , assigning a different color to each of them , and asked them to produce a feature based on their emotional and creative response to the given color , later to be distributed in the form of podcasts . the four-minute film , shot by trent &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; in blomkamp 's usual handheld camera mockumentary style , deals with an israeli military robot gone rogue .